narration_text: #C C pours soup round on the plate
#C C holds the cooking pot with left hand and chopsticks on the right hand
#C C uses chopsticks to serve food from the cooking pot
#C C places the chopsticks on the cooking pot
#C C places the cooking pot on top of the gas cooker
#C C moves the plate and bowl with both hands
#C C lets go of the plate and bowl
